The restaurant: The setup of Swish is interesting.
At Swish, you're seated at a long, u-shaped counter with a hot pot placed in front of each diner.
Unfortunately, the pot is placed in an awkward location, forcing the diner to reach up over the bar, and then at a downward angle, to swish their food.
