I arrive at Swish a bit earlier than my partners tonight.
This far from the Asian markets on Spring Mountain, I'm on high alert for flim flam.
After a quick stop in the restroom (clean, but no hot water at the sink tonight), I take a seat and let my server know that the investigation will include two others.
